                    <h1 class="domdom">08</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/838">Alice In The Cities  (1974)</a></h1>

                    <h2>8 Jan 2012, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>After brief encounter with an elusive American woman Phillip a roving German reporter reluctantly accepts temporary custody of little Alice. Their friendship grows while traveling through European cities on a search for the girl's grandmother. Inventive and witty, Wenders reflects on the influences of American pop culture on postwar Europe. </p>

                    <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/838">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

                </section>
