                    <h1 class="domdom">18</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/841">Nick&#39;s Film - Lightning Over Water (1980)</a></h1>

                    <h2>18 Jan 2012, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>The American director Nicholas Ray, mostly known for Rebel Without a Cause, is dying slowly of terminal cancer yet he stays at home with his closest friends. Ray reflects on a lifetime of accomplishments, failures and compromises, and reminisces about Joan Crawford, James Dean and many other Hollywood stars.</p>

                    <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/841">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

